title: European Union Natural Gas Imports From Russia
description: Natural Gas Imports from Russia in European Union decreased to 132008 Terajoule in August from 141254 Terajoule in July of 2022. Natural Gas Imports from Russia in European Union averaged 271635.41 Terajoule from 2008 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 500361 Terajoule in December of 2010 and a record low of 63032 Terajoule in February of 2015. This page includes a chart with historical data for European Union Natural Gas Imports From Russia.
author: EUROSTAT
